info:
岗位职责：
Translation of Standard Operating Procedures;
Maintains stock control in the laboratory and bring  consumables and reagents;
Carries out housekeeping and equipment checks as appropriate to ensure that laboratory compliance is maintained at all times, 5S;
Actively maintains a clean, tidy and safe work environment；
Informs relevant personnel immediately when any deviation has occurred during routine testing;
Take other tasks as assigned by line manager

任职要求：
Major in Microbiology, Biological Sciences or relevant scientific subject is preferred
Good at English reading and writing;
Ability to complete documentation (both handwritten and electronic) neatly and accurately; 
0-2 years experience in a scientific laboratory role, ideally within a contract testing laboratory environment；
Working hard, results driven

职责描述：
1.为用户提供全面的接待体验，并不断增强现有用户品牌忠诚度;
2.准确地向用户传递并耐心讲解蔚来品牌与产品，并传递蔚来价值观;
3.根据销售策略和团队目标，制定工作计划，完成销售;
4.开展营销活动，不断创新、积极主动地吸引潜在用户

任职要求：
1.在校生，大专及以上学历;
2.对销售数据敏感，优秀的数据分析能力和逻辑分析能力;
3.优秀的沟通能力和谈判能力，良好的自我管理能力及自我学习能力;
4.抗压能力强，能够应在高速发展的环境中开展销售管理工作，达到公司业结指标要求;
5.认可蔚来汽车的创业公司文化，具备创业公司必要的心理素质;
6.C1及以上驾照，驾驶技术熟练
